    "Fang found ChatGPT more helpful than popular programming websites like CSDN or GitHub.",
    "In contrast to fruitless searches on forums, Fang could input source code or issues into ChatGPT and receive specific and tailored responses, saving significant time.",
    "Fourthly, \"human-like interaction\" was mentioned by 4 students.",
